Package com.prckt.krowemarf.services.UserManagerServices

Interface _User

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    User

    public interface _User
extends java.rmi.Remote, java.io.Serializable
    Define the User in the framework. The hash field represent the password of the user. This class extends the UnicastRemoteObject, allows to remotely access instances of this method
